han1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">shān</a> ]</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">mountain, hill, peak</span></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<hr><span id=\"purpleculture_examples\">①(灿烂)光彩，耀眼，如“阳光灿灿”。亦简称“灿”，如“灿若晨星”。<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E7%81%BF%E7%83%82\" class=\"sword\">灿烂</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-can4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">càn</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-lan4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">làn</a> ]: to glitter; brilliant; splendid<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E7%81%BF%E8%8B%A5%E7%B9%81%E6%98%9F\" class=\"sword\">灿若繁星</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-can4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">càn</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-ruo4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">ruò</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-fan2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">fán</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-xing1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">xīng</a> ]: bright as a multitude of stars (idiom); extremely able talent<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E7%81%BF%E7%83%82%E5%A4%BA%E7%9B%AE\" class=\"sword\">灿烂夺目</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-can4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">càn</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-lan4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">làn</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-duo2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">duó</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-mu4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">mù</a> ]: dazzling; brilliant (idiom)</span>\n<hr>\n<div>\n  <div>\n    <div><span class=\"tc\">(Trad.: 燦)</span></div><b>Chinese Definition:</b>\n    <div><b>Pictophonetic</b>: <span class=\"semantic\"><a class=\"dictips\">山</a></span> indicates the sound; <span class=\"phonetic\"><a class=\"dictips\">火</a></span> (fire) conveys the meaning.</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div>HSK: 6</div>\n<div>Freq: 2591</div>\n<div><span style=\"color:tomato\">Chinese</span>: The fire mountains, or volcanoes, must be the most brilliant of all mountains.</div>\n<hr>\n<div><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Meaning:</span> brilliant<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Hanzi:</span> 燦<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Story:</span> After the evening rice, the guest set out to entertain the children of the house with a brilliant show. He pulled a wand seemingly from out of his crotch and suddenly it appeared to be on fire! Ohs and ahs ensued.<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Kind:</span> simplified<br><img src=\"29158.gif\"></div>\n<div>\n  <hr>\n</div>\n<div id=\"hanziyuan\">\n  <div class=\"etymology-nav\" id=\"&#x707F;\">\n    <div class=\"alert alert-success etymology-alert m-0\" role=\"alert\"></div>\n    <div class=\"row bg-info border-purple border-top mx-0 row-eq-height\" id=\"E00533\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-4 p-0\">\n        <div class=\"p-1\">\n          <p></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in your browser 繁体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x71E6;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in Unicode standard 繁体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=71E6\" target=\"_blank\">U+71E6</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-71E6\"></p>\n          <p><b>Older traditional characters 旧繁体字/异体字:</b> Not exist</p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in your browser 简体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x707F;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in Unicode standard 简体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=707F\" target=\"_blank\">U+707F</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-707F\"></p>\n          <p><b>Main pronunciation 主要发音:</b> c&#xE0;n</p>\n          <p><b>Other pronunciations 其它发音:</b> Not exists.</p>\n          <p><b>Original meaning 本义:</b> Meaning illuminating.</p>\n          <p><b>English senses 英语理解:</b> vivid, illuminating; bright</p>\n          <p><b>Usage example 用法举例:</b> &#x71E6;&#x721B; c&#xE0;n l&#xE0;n (glorious)</p>\n          <p><b>Importance by frequency 常用频率:</b> 2636</p>\n          <p><b>Shuowen 说文解字:</b> &#x71E6;&#x7224;&#x660E;&#x701E;&#x8C8C;&#x5F9E;&#x706B;&#x7CB2;&#x8072;</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Character decomposition 字形分解 <a href=\"https://dixin.github.io/Etymology/decomposition-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br>Compound &#x71E6;&#xD;&#xA;from fire &#x706B; hu&#x1D2; and &#xD;&#xA;phonetic rice-can &#x7CB2; c&#xE0;n &#xD;&#xA;phonetic mountain &#x5C71; sh&#x101;n&#xD;&#xA;A019 &#x707F;[&#x71E6;]&#xD;&#xA;new-char &#x707F;.</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Decomposition notes 字形分解说明 <a href=\"https://dixin.github.io/Etymology/decomposition-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Simplification rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b> A019 &#x707F;[&#x71E6;]</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Simplification rule explained <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br>new-char &#xD;&#xA;phonetic-phonetic &#x5C71;&#x7CB2;&#xD;&#xA;&#x5C71;&#x7CB2;</p>\n          <p><b>Variant rule :</b> C000</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Variant rule clarification <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Applied rules <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p><b>New font rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p><a target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"p-1 bg-primary col-md-9 col-sm-8 etymology-result\" id=\"etymologyCharacters\">\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known oracle characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known bronze characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span> Seal characters (1)</h3>\n        <ul class=\"list-inline list-unstyled\">\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-S07392.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>灿</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>灿<br>（燦）<br>càn<br>〔灿烂〕光彩，耀眼，如“阳光灿灿”。亦简称“灿”，如“灿若晨星”。<br>（燦）<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>灿</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［càn］<br>［《廣韻》蒼案切，去翰，清。］<br>“灿1”的繁体字。<br>(1)明亮貌。<br>(2)鲜艳貌；鲜明貌。<br>(3)明白，清楚。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>灿</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【巳集中】【火字部】　燦； 康熙笔画：17； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/0666.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页666第26</span></a><br>【唐韻】【集韻】【韻會】倉案切【正韻】倉晏切，?音粲。【說文】燦爛，明瀞貌。　又【集韻】通作粲。【詩·唐風】角枕粲兮，錦衾爛兮。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>灿</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>灿</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>：指灿烂、光彩、鲜明、耀眼、明白、清楚。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">Bright<br>Basic explanation of words<br>Bright<br>(Can)<br>càn<br>[Bright] Brilliant, dazzling, such as \"sunshine.\" Also referred to as \"Can\", such as \"Can as the morning star\".<br>(Can)<br>Bright<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［càn］<br>[\"Guangyun\" Cang case cut, go to Han, Qing. ]<br>Traditional characters of \"灿1\".<br>(1) Bright appearance.<br>(2) Bright appearance; bright appearance.<br>(3) Understand and be clear.<br>Bright<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Si Collection] [Fire Word Department] 　Can; Kangxi Strokes: 17; Page Number: Page 666 Page 26<br>[Tang Yun] [Ji Yun] [Rhyme Meeting] Cang Yan cut [Zheng Yun] Cang Yan cut,? Yin Chan. [Speaking text] Brilliant, bright appearance.　[Jiyun] It is full of charm. 【Poetry·Tang Style】The corner pillow is embarrassing and the quilt is rotten.<br>Bright<br>Source glyph<br>Bright<br>Name meaning<br>: Refers to brilliant, brilliance, vivid, dazzling, clear and clear.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148273811223709.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148273811223709.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148273811223709.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">灿<br>形声字。火表意,像火苗溅出火星状,表示火光耀眼;粲(can)表声,粲是精米,有鲜明美好义,表示火光明亮为燦。简<br>体字从火、山(shan )声,表示火焰高大如小山必灿然。本义是<br>càn<br>光彩耀眼。<br>光彩耀眼:~然」光~「金~~。<br>~烂~然 光~ ~然一新 光辉~烂<br>燦,燦灿<br>楷</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">Яркий<br>Пиктофонетические символы.<br>Огонь означает, что это похоже на пламя, вырывающееся из искр, что означает, что огонь ослепляет; звук банки (can), который представляет собой полированный рис, имеет яркое и красивое значение, что означает, что свет огня яркий и блестящий.<br>В упрощенных иероглифах звук огня и горы (шань) означает, что пламя достигает высоты холма и будет ярким.<br>Первоначальный смысл - блеск и ослепление.<br>Блеск ослепительный: ~ пробежал \"свет ~\" золотой ~~.<br>~ Rotten ~ Ranguang ~~ Ranyixin Shining ~ Гнилой<br>Может, Канкан<br>Кай</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">càn</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div>сияющий, ясный, сверкающий, блестящий, яркий</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=灿\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=灿&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=灿\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=灿\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=灿\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/灿\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=灿\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/灿\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=灿&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#灿\">Char lookup site</a></p>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"火","pinyins":["Huo3","huo3"]},{"glyph":"山","pinyins":["Shan1","shan1"]}],"isMentionedAt__hanziyuan_without_charactersWithCo